    ----------------------------------------------------------------------
    | 31                 20|19       15|14       12|11       7|6        0|
    |         csr          |    rs1    |   funct3  |    rd    |  opcode  |
    |     source/dest      | uimm[4:0] |   CSRRWI  |   dest   |  SYSTEM  |
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    CSRRWI behavior likes below and it needs to work atomically
    
    x[rd] = CSRs[csr]; CSRs[csr] = uimm
    
